FIGHTC.original: If the crowd sides with you, in can help out in a tight spot.
FIGHTC.translated: If the crowd sides with you, in can help out in a tight spot.

FIGHTC.original: To get the crowd on your side try to showboat by pressing LB or perform counters.
FIGHTC.translated: To get the crowd on your side try to showboat by pressing LB or perform counters.

FIGHTC.original: FIGHT CLUB ~n~ ~n~ The goal is beat down anyone who steps up and challenge you.~n~ ~n~ There are 7 ranks increasing in difficulty. Maim your way to the top.
FIGHTC.translated: FIGHT CLUB ~n~ ~n~ The goal is beat down anyone who steps up and challenge you.~n~ ~n~ There are 7 ranks increasing in difficulty. Maim your way to the top.

FIGHTC.original: The fight is over, you have now made the next rank.
FIGHTC.translated: The fight is over, you have now made the next rank.
